---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Wedding Invitations | Downloadable Wedding Invitation Templates"
  description="Browse downloadable wedding invitations, editable wedding invitation suites, RSVP cards, details cards, and printable wedding stationery templates."
>
  <main>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container content">
        <p class="eyebrow">Wedding invitations</p>
        <h1>Downloadable wedding invitations for a polished celebration.</h1>
        <p class="lead">Find coordinated wedding invitation templates designed to make your stationery feel cohesive, beautiful, and easy to customize.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container content">
        <h2>What is included in a wedding invitation suite?</h2>
        <p>A wedding invitation suite usually includes the main invitation, RSVP card, details card, and optional matching pieces like menu cards, thank you cards, programs, and wedding signs.</p>
        <ul class="list">
          <li>Main wedding invitation template</li>
          <li>RSVP card template</li>
          <li>Details card template</li>
          <li>Optional menu cards, thank you cards, and signage</li>
          <li>Editable files for easy customization</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">Shop by style</p>
        <h2>Popular wedding invitation styles</h2>
        <div class="grid">
          <a class="card" href="/wedding-invitation-suites/minimalist-weddings/">
            <h3>Minimalist Wedding Invitations</h3>
            <p>Simple, modern layouts with clean typography, soft spacing, and timeless details.</p>
          </a>
          <a class="card" href="/wedding-invitation-suites/mid-century-modern-weddings/">
            <h3>Mid-Century Wedding Invitations</h3>
            <p>Warm colors, retro shapes, and playful design details for stylish couples.</p>
          </a>
          <a class="card" href="/wedding-invitation-suites/black-and-white-weddings/">
            <h3>Black & White Wedding Invitations</h3>
            <p>Classic downloadable wedding invitation templates with elegant contrast and a timeless look.</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
